Since elif "Jon" will always be true so access to any user is granted
Solution
You can use any one method below
Fast
if name in ["Kevin", "Jon", "Inbar"]:
    print("Access granted.")
else:
    print("Access denied.")
Slow
if name == "Kevin" or name == "Jon" or name == "Inbar":
    print("Access granted.")
