You could make use of a single regex with 2 capture groups to match the key and the value.
((?:\bNOT\s+)?\w+)\s+IN\s+\('([^()]*)'\)
See the regex demo.
The pattern matches:
( Capture group 1
(?:\bNOT\s+)? Optionally match the word NOT followed by 1+ whitespace chars
