   |                        ----------- borrow of `number_list` occurs here
...
8  |     number_list = vec![102, 34, 6000, 89, 54, 2, 43, 8];
   |     ^^^^^^^^^^^ assignment to borrowed `number_list` occurs here
9  |
10 |     println!("The largest number is {}", largest_nbr);
