Note that this will still return false, as there is no document at the path message/JryeL6uzGRh86RiY5SXtn58fpup1-JryeL6uzGRh86RiY5SXtn58fpup1 in your database. The Firebase console show the path in italics to indicate that there is no document there, but there are subcollection.
